Title: Fail Fast on Concordion Run Command ConcordionRunner->ConcordionRunner:runLeaf() ConcordionRunner->FixtureRunner:run() FixtureRunner->Concordion: process(fixture) Concordion->Specification:process() Specification->SpecificationCommand:execute() SpecificationCommand->CommandCall: getChildren().
processSequentially() CommandCall->ThrowableCatchingDecorator: execute() ThrowableCatchingDecorator->RunCommand: execute() RunCommand->DefaultConcordionRunner: result = execute
(resource, href) Note right of DefaultConcordionRunner: Finds JUnit class DefaultConcordionRunner-->DefaultConcordionRunner: junitResult =
runTestClass(concordionClass) Note over DefaultConcordionRunner: Assuming test
class fails with
FailFastException DefaultConcordionRunner-->DefaultConcordionRunner: decodeJUnitResult
(concordionClass, jUnitResult) Note right of DefaultConcordionRunner: If test failed due to
FailFastException, throw it DefaultConcordionRunner-->RunCommand: throw FailFastException RunCommand-->ThrowableCatchingDecorator: throw FailFastException ThrowableCatchingDecorator->ResultRecorder: record(EXCEPTION) ThrowableCatchingDecorator->ResultRecorder: recordFailFastException ThrowableCatchingDecorator-->SpecificationCommand: throw FailFastException FixtureRunner->ResultSummary: assertIsSatisfied(fixture) ResultSummary->FixtureState:assertIsSatisfied() FixtureState-->ConcordionRunner: throw new AssertionError
